Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧妳們能夠度過此次難關
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人也該受到教訓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的事情現在才要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星逼近，世界動盪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能讓那些野蠻人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再對本國和世界恣意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要引導HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓此次的祭典成功完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便可以讓這個日之本再度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接以秀真國的身份\N所創造出來的繁榮時期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.18,0:00:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜之王即將覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰姬流下眼淚越多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君就愈歡喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好記住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得有所遺漏地進行祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈利就…消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重視的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主們\N看來妳們的宴會挺愉快的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!不可以爬到那麼高的地方!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能留你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝕已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們必須打倒的對象…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳們彼此的心之子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，時刻已到!祭典開始了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳的心中有著思念之情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這塊令人敬畏又想詛咒的\N封印之地上起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME們啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.11,0:02:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17話 說謊的雙唇\N簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17話 說謊的雙唇\N藉著國家認可不對外輸出\N不對內輸入的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方莊園就可以擅自支配國司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，自己的領土自己守護
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此需要武力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後就會聯繫到\N所謂武士的產生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是要妳們彼此對打而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用心之子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那伴隨著妳們\N對最重視對象的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一同成長的怪物對打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒心之子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果心之子被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該HiME最重視的人就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真用心預習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從小茜那裡聽來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個我可是有說過喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"要戰鬥的話，妳就非得賭上\N妳最重視的事物"這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…和也同學是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單說來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，是誰把門給鎖上了？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像不小心弄錯\N把鎖扣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天從早上開始\N就不斷犯這種小錯耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，有什麼事情\N就馬上跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人在那裡\N扭扭捏捏地煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定都盡往壞處想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳們本身\N因為某些原因被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們的心之子，還有最重視的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然會消失喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要守護重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就只有戰鬥\N並且獲得勝利一途
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會露出\N一副被神給捨棄的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石上…老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一路打贏過來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…妳這麼快就進入狀況\N對我來說可真是方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們就會乖乖說\N"喔，原來如此"嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說笑了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳們還是得打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無可避免的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來妳們就是為此而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同學，妳委託我的史料\N「封印月報」 已夾帶附加檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待看到妳的論文 佐佐木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子沒情調
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們沒有發現那個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媛星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有妳們才能看到的那顆星星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也依然持續地逼近地面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司掌所有災禍的紅色星星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是接近過來\N也會馬上造成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠控制媛星的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有最後得勝的唯一HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其心之子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們必須在\N那個媛星衝撞地表之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選出那一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒做到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本還不當一回事的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情誰會信啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來為什麼我們要做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是妳們的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為HiME的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有世界是否能夠繁榮的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在控制媛星的HiME的力量上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是叫我們要\N為了這個而犧牲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是該說是相對的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後獲勝的人\N可以得到很強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去跟不在這邊的人說明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣…該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去問理事長!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳沒來上課，有點擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有雪之跟命仔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一下好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？理事長還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回來之後\N我打算馬上去找她問清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會有事吧？那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心啦，我們是伙伴吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是HiME戰隊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有未知的HiME存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然人數有點不足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，HiME總共有12人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個幾乎是錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們不知道的HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還剩下2人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她們也不會那麼笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之，放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護妳和舞衣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，怎麼可以想動手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，我會再去調查看看\N那個炎小子說得是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有方法可以避免掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前\N要盡量避免輕率的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有我們，也要團結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有碰到修女和夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及奈緒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得要跟她們說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的，別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我們不會有事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要戰鬥的話\N妳就非得賭上妳最重視的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實知道的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道HiME是要互相殘殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是HiME的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叮囑我不可暴露女性身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是洩露出去就得消滅對方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的狀況還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然…既然你知道我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果晶無論如何都得做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去這麼多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有晶在的話，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經習慣於放棄了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我已經有點厭捲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼痛苦的病痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直說不出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，姊姊為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便把死掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是對你這個部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會，我才是，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明就有跟我說要敲門的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了吧!那是幻影!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，害你也得跟著請假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去上課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會守護你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我，該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，原來是武田同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬今天請假喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我又不是來找玖我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是找我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道武田是個好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照約定，這半年之間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絲毫沒有干涉楯那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他差不多應該也下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把他帶回我們社上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯好像有蠻多事情很忙的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就該引導迷途的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝這個，我對泡茶有點自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定比畫圖更好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢，好好喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣殺氣騰騰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才剛說不可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過小心反而會忽略掉腳邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候才更要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把球打過來的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，妳沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，妳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好妳沒受傷，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以像這樣很平常的跟妳說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得最近妳好像在躲我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，我並沒有躲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然差點做了那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒考慮妳的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然還是對楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可沒有對楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在蠻多狀況的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說不是講這種話的時候嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長!麻煩你照顧命!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到妳弟弟的捐贈者了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我來幫妳擦身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是換洗的睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，大色狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好，哥哥先退場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說要換手？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得狀況整個被打亂哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對巧海來說，真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後在各方面才是最辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要陪著詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會受傷是我造成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的很了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳不喜歡被人這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…妳要照顧巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光這樣就夠累人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼HiME啦，無依者的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又發生那麼大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但果然還是什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還放詩帆孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害她受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是得意忘形…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為自己一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定辦得到，然後一股腦蠻幹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後都會徹底失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在我總算…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的瞭解妳有多辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，那個，啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情沒替妳著想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你幹嘛突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子，不像你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必現在才說這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟詩帆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是從小就在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是哥哥，哥哥的叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說老實話，有時候真的會煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔，楯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒舒服點？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，你碰到誰了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒，只是到商店去看雜誌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到什麼好玩的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到妳會有興趣的玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"加油吧"這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是說的人還是聽的人\N都很不負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，妳啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠拼了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討，討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰塵跑進眼睛了，真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，得快點回去告訴巧海!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該讓黑曜少主醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，妳們還是得打
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無可避免的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來\N妳們就是為此而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.40,0:22:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:23:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開端\N哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開端\N你真的沒有跟誰見面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.62,0:23:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的裡外都不是人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.13,0:23:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像不太妙

Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很討厭被人強制做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是照我自己的方式\N一路過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為全部都是自己造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以其實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.52,0:24:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的從來沒想過我會當老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.39,0:24:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，當了之後\N才發現這其實是很快樂的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.46,0:24:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼當老師\N就是我命中註定的是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.13,0:24:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我\N憑著自己的意志選擇的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.77,0:24:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被大學踢出來是預料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是我選的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.28,0:24:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我絕對不相信\N命運這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.28,0:24:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的意志跟智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.95,0:24:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了超越命運而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.05,0:24:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用自己的手掌握明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠成為\N自己所期望的自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑自己的意志，自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


